    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "今から特別に聴いてもらいたい歌があります\n……LizNoirではない、あるアイドルの曲です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There is a song I would like you to listen to specially from now on.\n… It's not LizNoir‚ it's a song by some idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2,
      "endTime": 23.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15400.000000000002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "三年前の曲だけど……私の大好きな歌\n聴いてくれますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although it’s a song from 3 years ago… my favorite song.\nCould you please listen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8666666667,
      "endTime": 30.1828349413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。では、彼女と一緒に歌いたいと思います\nどうぞ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. Then I'll sing with her.\nCome on in――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9333333333,
      "endTime": 40.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10633.333333400004
        }
