    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央、大阪って、東京とは違った賑やかさがあるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ Osaka has a different liveliness than Tokyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2,
      "endTime": 50.404920578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、歴史的にも関西には関東と違った文化が――\nあら？　こころと愛は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ historically‚ the Kansai region had a different culture from the Kanto region…\nHuh? It's Kokoro and Ai‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6333333333,
      "endTime": 59.6739683355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "年少組なら、あそこで動画撮ってるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The youngest members were filming a video over there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.8666666667,
      "endTime": 62.6066667239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、愛、いいよいいよー、はい！\nそこで笑顔でＹ字バランスポーズをして！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes‚ Ai‚ Good‚ good~ Here!\nThere‚ smile and pose with the letter ‘Y’!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8666666667,
      "endTime": 69.6005214374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "ええーっ！？　ネタっぽくない？\n恥ずかしいよ、こころー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~!? Doesn’t it seem like a joke?\nI’m embarrassed~‚ Kokoro~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7666666667,
      "endTime": 74.79210741050001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "愛はLizNoirのお笑い担当だからこれでいいの！\nほら、いつもの媚びたスマイルを！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai is in charge of LizNoir jokes‚ so it's okay!\nNow‚ with your usual charming smile~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.9666666667,
      "endTime": 81.5481918861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "それはこころの得意技でしょー！\nもー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s Kokoro’s specialty~!\nI hate it~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7333333333,
      "endTime": 85.66270586499999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "口では嫌だと言いながら、やってくれる愛が\nこころは愛おしい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro loves Ai\nwho does it even though saying 'I hate it'!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.0333333333,
      "endTime": 90.9589326299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "……あの子達は、あんなにはしゃいで\nライブの本番前だっていうのに、大した度胸ね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…They're so excited\nEven before the live performance‚ what a nerve…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.3,
      "endTime": 98.00592658910001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "もぐっもぐ、ごくん。二人は大阪を満喫してるよね\nあっ、このたこ焼き美味しいよ、莉央も食べなよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "munch munch‚ munching. The two are enjoying Osaka.\nAh‚ this takoyaki is delicious‚ Rio‚ try it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2333333333,
      "endTime": 107.5322657692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "……いつの間に買ったの？\n貴方も負けずに満喫してるわよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "… When did you buy it?\nYou are enjoying it just as much…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7333333333,
      "endTime": 112.2101827679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくのツアーだからね、少しはいいじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been a while‚ so wouldn't it be okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4666666667,
      "endTime": 117.2894785563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、たくましくなったのはいいけど緊張感は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ha‚ it's good to be stronger‚ but the tension is――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5,
