      "text": "なんでもないわ。さっ、息抜きはもうおしまい\n愛、こころも会場に戻るわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nothing. Okay‚ break time is over now.\nAi and Kokoro‚ let's go back to the concert hall.",
        "id": ""
      },
