      "text": "妹の琴乃が出て優勝したけど\nそれで彼女は救われたのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her younger sister Kotono competed and won\nbut was she saved?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.6333333333,
      "endTime": 270.6545257071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
