      "text": "どうかしら、喜んでるとも思うし\n悔しがってるかもしれないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder what it would be like. She might be happy\nor she might be angry",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.8333333333,
      "endTime": 276.4207765978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
