      "text": "今の僕達を見たら、どう思うだろう\n一言でいいから、感想がほしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What would she think if you saw us now?\nI'd like to hear‚ even if it's just one word.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 282.5666666667,
      "endTime": 290.5567516524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
